<h3 id=3D"Influencer,Retailer&amp;Distributor:DataEnrichment-Influencerprof=
ileenrichment(Mason,Architect,Engineer)">Influencer profile enrichment (Mas=
on, Architect, Engineer)</h3>
<p>On every visit, a detailed and systematic enrichment of the retailer=E2=
=80=99s profile is carried out focusing on the following aspects:</p>
<hr>
<p>Addition of fields related to Retailer, Influencer, Distributor:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>PII Info field:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>PAN card,</p></li>
<li>
<p>mobile,</p></li>
<li>
<p>email,</p></li>
<li>
<p>Address fields</p></li>
<li>
<p>Pincode</p></li>
</ol></li>
<li>
<p>Account Segmentation Info fields:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Annual turnover (in Cr.),</p></li>
<li>
<p>Monthly Potential (in MT)</p></li>
</ol></li>
<li>
<p>Fields for profile enrichment:</p></li>
</ol>
