<li>
<p>TMT</p></li>
<li>
<p>Paints</p></li>
<li>
<p>Cement</p></li>
<li>
<p>RMC</p></li>
</ol></li>
<li>
<p>For each Category, there needs to be provision to select</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Brands (Category wise Brands are defined in sheet, Categories: TMT, AAC =
Blocks, Cement : <a class=3D"external-link" data-card-appearance=3D"inline"=
