4-4a9f-b87b-bb5b6f159356" data-media-type=3D"file" height=3D"292"></span>
<p></p>
<hr>
<p><strong>Influencer Association to Projects and Sites</strong></p>
<p>An Influencer record should have an association with Multiple address (c=
hild object) with Projects and Sites</p>
<ol start=3D"7">
<li>
<p>Projects and sites also need to be related Objects to Influencer.</p></l=
i>
<li>
<p>There should be checkin and checkout mechanism in place for each Project=
 and site level</p></li>
<li>
<p>Current major projects &amp; Site level, we need to capture</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Categories, Brands, Tonnage,.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Addresses (All the information capture should be similar to that of site=
 information capture which is existing)</p></li>
<li>
<p>Option to Check in and Check out at Project and Site level</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ol>
<hr>
